               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa ʾaślǝṭi, Lectionary for the entire year (fols. 3r-21v)
 -
                     Bārǝkanna ʾǝgziʾo… “Bless us, O Lord…” (Blessing prayer) (fols. 18r-20r)
                     
 Additio 1.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="3r" to="21v"/>
                     <title>Maṣḥafa ʾaslǝṭi</title>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
                        <locus from="3r" to="17v"/>
                        <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1917Mashaf#year">Maṣḥafa ʾaślǝṭi, Lectionary for the entire year</title>                                                
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
