                                 <dim unit="leaf">10</dim>
                                 <locus target="#10"/>
                                 <locus from="13r" to="22v"/> II(10/fols. 13r-22v)</item>
                           </list>
                        </collation>
                        <condition key="deficient">Deficient.
 The Ms. is worn.
 The front
                           and the back boards are broken and crudely repaired by mean of vegetal
                           threads.
 The sewing is damaged.
 Some fols. are damaged by
                           water, esp. <locus from="15" to="22">15-22</locus>.
 The text is
                           abraded in fols 13v-14r and elsewhere.
 The red ink is mostly
                           faded.
 A tear is crudely amended in <locus target="#13">13</locus>.</condition>
                     </supportDesc>
                     <layoutDesc>
                        <layout columns="1" writtenLines="17">
                           <dimensions unit="mm">
                              <height>100</height>
